OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781545682
OL,3,CSentence of man who killed Henry Nowak
OL,4,Creferred to court of appeal
OL,6,FThe sentence given to the man who
OL,7,Ffatally stabbed Henry Nowak has been
OL,8,Freferred to the Court of Appeal.
OL,10,FSolicitor General Ellie Reeves KC
OL,11,Fapplied for the jail term given to 23-
OL,12,Fyear-old Vickrum Digwa to be
OL,13,Freconsidered under the Unduly Lenient
OL,14,FSentence scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781545682
OL,3,CSentence of man who killed Henry Nowak
OL,4,Creferred to court of appeal
OL,6,FShe said: "This case horrified me, and
OL,7,FI know that feeling is shared by the
OL,8,FBritish public. It is right that
OL,9,Fdifficult questions need to be
OL,10,Fanswered about the way the police
OL,11,Fhandled Henry's Nowak's murder, while
OL,12,Fmy role is to review Digwa's sentence
OL,13,Ffor his crimes.
OL,15,F"After careful consideration, I have
OL,16,Ftaken the decision to refer this case
OL,17,Fto the Court of Appeal.
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781545682
OL,3,CSentence of man who killed Henry Nowak
OL,4,Creferred to court of appeal
OL,6,F"No sentence can ever undo the
OL,7,Fdevastation that Henry's family have
OL,8,Fsuffered, or fill the void left by his
OL,9,Floss. But I hope this referral goes
OL,10,Fsome way towards bringing them the
OL,11,Fjustice they deserve."
OL,13,FDigwa was jailed for life to serve a
OL,14,Fminimum of 21 years for stabbing Mr
OL,15,FNowak with a ceremonial knife with a
OL,16,F21cm blade prosecutors said was a
OL,17,Fkirpan, which he carried as part of
OL,18,Fhis Sikh religion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
