CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781545682
OL,3,CSentence of man who killed Henry Nowak
OL,4,Creferred to court of appeal
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage from the
OL,7,Fincident appeared to show Mr Nowak,
OL,8,Fwho had received two stab wounds on
OL,9,Fthe back his legs and a fatal wound to
OL,10,Fhis heart, pleading, "I've been
OL,11,Fstabbed" and "I can't breathe" while
OL,12,Fbeing handcuffed.
OL,14,FThe finance student was handcuffed
OL,15,Fafter being fatally stabbed with the
OL,16,Fknife in Southampton on December 3
OL,17,F2025 by 23-year-old Vickrum Digwa, who
OL,18,Ffalsely accused him of being drunk and
OL,19,Flaunching a racist attack.
OL,26,@rD@VOUsD@HO]sD@NOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
